---
Title: Governing Under Heaven
Author: Chuang Tzu
Source:
  - Title: The Book of Chuang Tzu
    Chapter: 7
    Page: 61
    Translator: Martin Palmer, Elizabeth Breuilly, Chang Wai Ming, Jay Ramsay
    Publisher: Arkana
    Copyright: 1996 ICOREC
    ISBN: 0140194886
Tags:
  - separation
  - path
---
Let your heart journey in simplicity.
Be one with that which is beyond definition.
Let all things be as they are.
Have no personal views.
This is how everything under heaven is ruled.
